To get started planning a fulfilling career that does a lot of good, go to https://80000hours.org/inanutshell for your free career guide.

Time’s running out! Secure your Survival Kit for the Future before it’s too late! Only on the kurzgesagt shop: https://shop.kgs.link/SurvivalKit

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sources-fever/

Fever feels bad. So we take medication to suppress it – but is this a good idea? It turns out fever is one of the oldest defenses against disease. 
What exactly is a fever, and how does it make your immune defense stronger? Should you take a pill to combat it?
